	<a href="//dotearth.blogs.nytimes.com/?module=BlogMain&action=Click&region=Header&pgtype=Blogs&version=Blog Post&contentCollection=Opinion"><div id="logo" class="archived-blog-post"><div class="w75 left site-header-logo"><img src="https://static01.nyt.com/images/blogs_v3/dotearth/dotearth75.gif" alt="Dot Earth"/></div><div class="site-title">Dot Earth</div><div class="site-description">New York Times blog</div></div></a>    </div>
